    "long_instructions": "### Partner Game\r\nFind out what others think of your songs! \r\n\r\n**Do This:**\r\n- Tell your partners who your three characters are and describe the character's personalities.\r\n- Play one of your Walk-Up songs without saying which character it belongs to.\r\n- Allow your partner to match the song to a character.\r\n- Ask them to explain their choice.\r\n- If they guess wrong, listen to their explanation and adjust your code to make the song fit the character better.\r\n- Repeat with new partners until someone guesses all three correctly!",
